OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early morning mist and fog
OL,6,Fwill clear quickly as low cloud in the
OL,7,Feast fades. Another bright and sunny
OL,8,Fday follows with temperatures expected
OL,9,Fto be slightly higher than Thursday.
OL,10,FUV levels will also be high through
OL,11,Fthe day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA very clear night to come
OL,14,Fwith calm winds expected. Temperatures
OL,15,Flikely to fall close to freezing,
OL,16,Fforming a grass from in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
