OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAnother bright and sunny day
OL,6,Fto start the weekend. Sunshine could
OL,7,Fturn hazy into the afternoon in
OL,8,Fplaces, but will feel very warm in the
OL,9,Flight winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStaying
OL,12,Fwarm and sunny into next week with
OL,13,Flight winds. Likely to be more cloud
OL,14,Fon Sunday which will allow
OL,15,Ftemperatures to dip slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
